1
00:00:05,853 --> 00:00:08,975
Hi everyone, welcome to Evolving God of War's combat for a new perspective.

2
00:00:09,876 --> 00:00:13,878
Thanks for coming by on the last day of GDC, after what was I'm sure an exciting but very

3
00:00:13,918 --> 00:00:14,498
tiring week.

4
